{
  "stem": "11272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I fell in line with my group, and they ordered me to go to another area, where I was given a striped uniform and wooden clogs-- no underwear, nothing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was still very, very cold in the Silesian mountains, and I was freezing, so tried to move around to get a little blood flowing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they started marching us out from there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as they marched us past the women's section, I heard cries-- Yankele!",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yankele!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I recognized the voice, but I looked over, and, you know, I saw probably 100 people with handkerchief and a striped frock over them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know whether they were women or men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I came closer, it turned out it was the voice of Mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, again by nature, I forgot the beating I got.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I wanted to go and just to touch her and just to kiss her if I can.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But again, the kapo and the SS men just almost beat me to death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, they gave me a good, swift kick in my shoulder that sometimes it still hurts.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From there, they marched me to the main camp of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the following day, they put me on trucks to take me to Auschwitz III, what is called Buna or Buna Werke.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The camp over there is-- is-- is beyond human description.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I'll give you a good example.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Elie Wiesel, when he got his honorary doctorate at Emory, I picked him up-- he and I are very close.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He and I went to all the camps together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were liberated together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we talked in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I asked him, when I picked him up at 5:00 in the morning, I said Elie, I heard you talk.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
